{"tid":1508740,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"英國智庫報告看BNO","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:51:06.000Z","uid":229201,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"63db68fc6193184ba551d85debffa060a89d42c7","tid":1508740,"uid":229201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"從Adam Smith Institute報告看BNO之謎 <br />\n就在香港反送中運動峰迴路轉之際, 英國出現要幫BNO (British National (Overseas) ) 護照持有人升級至英國公民 (British Citizen, BC) 的聲音. 我先將結論拋出來:<br />\n<br />\n1. 其目的為增加英國公民在港人數, 提升英國在港的影響力;<br />\n2. 維持英國在國際社會的形象, 以吸納香港人才及資本;<br />\n3. BNO從來都是權宜的國籍身份, 本質上是一種政治工具.<br />\n<br />\nBNO從97回歸前就是一個問題, 中英兩國一直避談. 2008年, Lord Goldsmith出了一份國籍檢討報告, 言明因為中英聯合聲明規範, 所以BNO權利不能變更. 不過, 有網友自此開始在網絡論壇討論BNO. 到了2015年銅鑼灣書店事件後, 港人國籍問題再被喚起. 今年3月起反送中運動不斷升溫, 英國政府卻一直袖手.<br />\n<br />\n不過, 從7月開始, 英國輿論 &ndash; 從每日快報, 衛報, 觀察者, 甚至太陽報紛紛鼓吹英國政府應給予BNO持有者BC身份. 值得一提的是英國智庫Adam Smith Institute在8月15日出了一份名為Doing Our Duty的研究報告, 建議英國政府應將BNO權利擴大至與BC同等, 因為若BNO人成為BC, 這&rdquo;將會促使中國和平地行事&rdquo; (p. 6), 香港人可以&rdquo;在自由的環境下生活, 而中國則失去一整代人, 英國會得到道德和物質上的勝利&rdquo; (p. 7). 不只如此, 香港人&rdquo;人均收入高, 高學歷及具備專業技能, 對英國經濟會有實質益處&rdquo; (p. 8). 最後, 英國幫BNO升級可顯示英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo; (p. 9). 這份報告暗示: a. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會使英國有理由介入香港事務, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就行) (結論1和3); b. 英國對香港的&rdquo;道義和責任&rdquo;乃建基在利益上, 尤其正值英國脫歐, 香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員 (結論2).<br />\n<br />\nBNO平權連署請願正進行著, 最後英國是否會修例將BNO變BC仍未知之數. 基本上, 中國愈要介入香港, 英國亦會有所跟進. 大國過招, 香港人並非只能選邊站. 最起碼, 我們能嘗試搞清楚它們的邏輯, 不在茫茫網海中迷失方向.<br />\n<br />\n(p.s. Simon Cheng案的發展將是英國是否為BNO平權的指標)<br />\n<br />\n英國智庫報告傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/56eddde762cd9413e151ac92/t/5d551c8cfd22760001587189/1565858960793/Doing+Our+Duty.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F56eddde762cd9413e151ac92%2Ft%2F5d551c8cfd22760001587189%2F1565858960793%2FDoing%2BOur%2BDuty.pdf&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=b28d5117\" target=\"_blank\">https://static1.squarespace.com/static/56eddde762cd9413e151ac92/t/5d551c8cfd22760001587189/1565858960793/Doing+Our+Duty.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066769?fbclid=IwAR2sM7Cng4cIkvHGpxLs7ntcthKZXW-2GPrZwga_1iuJsdwMT-d5t29nRvE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066769%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2sM7Cng4cIkvHGpxLs7ntcthKZXW-2GPrZwga_1iuJsdwMT-d5t29nRvE&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=c7182dd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066769%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2sM7Cng4cIkvHGpxLs7ntcthKZXW-2GPrZwga_1iuJsdwMT-d5t29nRvE&h=c65fd3fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066769?fbclid=IwAR2sM7Cng4cIkvHGpxLs7ntcthKZXW-2GPrZwga_1iuJsdwMT-d5t29nRvE</a>"},{"pid":"1c5f25e0bf2e535c8755c4c540bc4a9a0163bda2","tid":1508740,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0235fd50c9379aeb55de4d0671f02d25eea24917","tid":1508740,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=72a1ee70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=1ba1bbdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=eca15619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"41078ef9af21ed6486fb6e466cc4b93987b2451d","tid":1508740,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:22:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe07c4607956b93a3c47bfaff4d6af647bd13997","tid":1508740,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"一個打工仔想宣布罷工，立此民調望各位網友號召全港打工仔同老闆幫我個人罷工行動作一個決策參考！<br />\n升級罷工，全民自決，網民發起問卷調查！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508197</a><br />\n<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;🍳👨🏻&zwj;🏭👩🏻&zwj;🚒👩🏻&zwj;🔬👩🏼&zwj;🏫👷&zwj;♂👨🏼&zwj;🎤👨🏾&zwj;🔧👩🏻&zwj;💼👨🏻&zwj;💻<br />\n一分鐘 填一填｜ <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe-vNbJsdOviermmz3NGLPkXZN0GvOPKkkTrDb8QxaeS35C7w/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe-vNbJsdOviermmz3NGLPkXZN0GvOPKkkTrDb8QxaeS35C7w%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=a54f6969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe-vNbJsdOviermmz3NGLPkXZN0GvOPKkkTrDb8QxaeS35C7w/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a><br />\n<br />\n網民自發，全民參與，意見咨詢，決策參考。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpD40fE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpD40fE.jpg&h=6cea06ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dCmh2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dCmh2k.jpg&h=274a80cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a78b838fe0e1cbf75f739a63a681dd5999e46d0a","tid":1508740,"uid":19037,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:11:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=3b6f2a39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n想英國出手就聯署啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1552cb257ba3f79fd9a4120cf0503a40c64d78be","tid":1508740,"uid":301260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:51:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d320f8a4a03c390ae923a790e31bba74a9db19f","tid":1508740,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"319b36173079243cffd5f1e1deae1ffe3dd8fe49","tid":1508740,"uid":272795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37127f30bcc792733729300fef1f2f90424d89c2","tid":1508740,"uid":304769,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"BNO平權最後一件事（一定成功）（必看必推長文）（要人）(文宣入)<br />\n我們要採取更主動的方式來推動BNO平權，目前最實際的方法就是<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">大家聯合起來用xxx（到時結尾可以用連登編號聯署）位British Hongkonger的名義</span></ins></strong>來<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發信給1.英國首相 2.下議院議長 3.內政大臣 4.外交事務大臣 5.全體下議院議員</span></strong></ins>人手一封<br />\n在此請求英語超級好的入來（IELTS7.5+，writing6.5+）幫忙寫,當中<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須強調脫歐後香港人能幫助英國，因為脫歐才是目前英國最頭疼的事</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n內容如下：<br />\n1. 說之以理<br />\n對當前<br />\na. 香港的概況，<br />\nb. 我們如何受到<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">迫害(HSBC,CX,Swire&hellip;&hellip;)</span></strong></ins>，<br />\nc. 英國政府對香港的道義責任，<br />\nd. BNO的詳細介紹，因為英國人絕大部分根本不清楚BNO是什麼東西，<br />\ne. 我們必須強調我們都<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">是忠君愛國的英國人</span></ins></strong>，<br />\nf. 目前<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我們的安全，自由和法治受到前所未有的嚴重威脅</span></strong></ins>，<br />\ng. 而<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有英國人都應該有權在安全，自由和法治和免於恐懼的環境下生活</span></strong></ins>的，<br />\nh. 這是<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>英國政府保護國民的責任</ins></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n2. 動之以情<br />\na. 我們必須強調我們都是<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">忠君愛國的英國人</span></strong></ins><br />\nb. 我們都是<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">奉行英國價值觀</span></strong></ins>，民主，自由，法治，廉潔，崇尚一以辯論為本的教育，政治和法治，崇尚獨立思考和批判性思考，重視個人基本權利和利益<br />\n3. 誘之以利<br />\na. 因為若BNO人成為BC, 這<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;將會促使中國和平地行事&rdquo; </span></strong></ins><br />\nb. 香港人可以&rdquo;在自由的環境下生活, 而中國則失去一整代人, <ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">英國會得到道德和物質上的勝利</span></strong></ins>&rdquo; <br />\nc. 不只如此,<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 香港人&rdquo;人均收入高, 高學歷及具備專業技能, 對英國經濟會有實質益處&rdquo; </span></strong></ins><br />\nd. 最後, 英國幫BNO升級可顯示<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo; </span></strong></ins><br />\ne. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></strong></ins>,<br />\nf. 正值英國脫歐, <ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員</span></strong></ins><br />\ng.香港比非常多的英聯邦國家（例如加拿大）更能保持英國制度，故此<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港大多專業人士和技術人員無需太多訓練即可完成註冊並投入英國工作</span></strong></ins>，萬一英國<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">脫歐後出現人手短缺，香港人可以幫上大忙</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n大家有補充請在下面留言"},{"pid":"7410472ff0d1ffc0b4dc3f667d6d63baf508f3d1","tid":1508740,"uid":229201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:35:59.000Z","msg":"push push"},{"pid":"4a3630dc47e8594a9e8d32d5a5ff8f94360493b6","tid":1508740,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"英國佬一定留左一手架 <br />\n<br />\n當初都唔想比香港共產黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5def970f2e4766d264f07f3c2aca04f753e0654","tid":1508740,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"