y died would not forgive us.」證明大家的表態係非常重要，千萬不要小看自己。報道亦肯定了五大訴求缺一不可，證明美方不會單憑林鄭耍小動作，而放棄對香港的關注和對港共的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n至為緊要是最尾那一段預告：<br />\n<br />\nProtesters have called for a demonstration at the U.S. consulate Saturday to support the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, a proposed bill that would strengthen U.S. backing for democratization and human rights in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n美方現正觀察林鄭電視講話後香港人的反應，如果我們在星期日的示威不夠熱烈，勢必予人一個錯誤的觀感，以為民情冷卻。所以我懇請大家，不只網上表態，也要用腳表態，在美國駐港領事館前，堅定促請美國國會通過《香港民主及人權法》。<br />\n<br />\n98必出，總動員呀"},{"pid":"6a7968e8f4b48293ab058a53e78b0da6d36f87f3","tid":1508740,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"快撚啲簽咗先啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=3b6f2a39\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"b19fa58d02e90bb9e332ed2d35b8b866eeeb0b78","tid":1508740,"uid":229201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59910fdecca69590aa4ff22a67f9ecc57d3b1b8c","tid":1508740,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"《洛杉磯時報》報道林鄭撤回修例時，有寫到大家轉載《凜冬烈火》的截圖：「If we accepted the government&rsquo;s conditions, our friends who&rsquo;ve already died would not forgive us.」證明大家的表態係非常重要，千萬不要小看自己。報道亦肯定了五大訴求缺一不可，證明美方不會單憑林鄭耍小動作，而放棄對香港的關注和對港共的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n至為緊要是最尾那一段預告：<br />\n<br />\nProtesters have called for a demonstration at the U.S. consulate Saturday to support the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, a proposed bill that would strengthen U.S. backing for democratization and human rights in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n美方現正觀察林鄭電視講話後香港人的反應，如果我們在星期日的示威不夠熱烈，勢必予人一個錯誤的觀感，以為民情冷卻。所以我懇請大家，不只網上表態，也要用腳表態，在美國駐港領事館前，堅定促請美國國會通過《香港民主及人權法》。<br />\n<br />\n98必出，總動員呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"係咪不需要不反對通